    {
      "text": "Final staging: Stage IIIA (T2b N2 M0). Molecular profiling (finalized 2024-10-10): KRAS G12C positive, EGFR wild-type, ALK rearrangement negative, ROS1 rearrangement negative, BRAF V600E negative, MET amplification negative. PD-L1 TPS 60% (high expression) by 22C3 IHC. No actionable driver mutations for first-line targeted therapy. Unresectable disease given N2 nodal involvement. Brain MRI (2024-09-25): no intracranial metastases."
